{"tid":1737311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(超重要) 11月24日早D投票! 政府極可能會半日停止投票!","createTime":"2019-11-19T02:30:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T03:55:54.000Z","uid":42139,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ea002385e1c96dafec36f205a7cbd4bace3cb9b3","tid":1737311,"uid":42139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:30:33.000Z","msg":"過去呢兩日發生既野令到香港人覺得好唔開心, 好失望<br />\n但我地要知道呢一場係一場持久運動, 任何幫到場運動都要做好佢! 唔好因為咁11月24日就灰左唔出黎投票!<br />\n<br />\n講返先,小弟做中資公司, 老闆今日叫左D員工入房問投票意向, 咁我老西都話投建制啦, 仲話不嬲投開民賤聯, 跟住老闆就叫我地果日早D投, 話晏左既唔知會唔會投唔到架咁...<br />\n<br />\n眾所周知掌心雷果D係一早一車一車咁送去投票, 我有理由相信政府會用埋D下三流手段, 可能去到中午1-2 點就唔俾人投, 跟住就剩係計朝早既票!<br />\n<br />\n所以請大家果日早D去投呀!!!!!"},{"pid":"037364895b9ed20322792cc097a903e0cf88ac69","tid":1737311,"uid":42139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:31:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1a3c211a2b091f275786fadc76cf16da95e3fa77","tid":1737311,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:53:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5d6090c8d05a8e8ab313b48b19d759b13e45184d","tid":1737311,"uid":42139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:20:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5900d2a7d8c2ffe198d6b7dcab76b41cdfb3aaf5","tid":1737311,"uid":42139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:21:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"46964f8f96e5077073fd9dcab7593906e0fb4f0c","tid":1737311,"uid":42139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:22:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cb6c01db14e7600265ef9dbf94c46eaa85d928d6","tid":1737311,"uid":42139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:22:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a250b56fb73f523c5f0dfbd40cfc6ac83f7a7fd6","tid":1737311,"uid":42139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:23:54.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"9fd42158cbe868d54ced133a6af0729112c1e810","tid":1737311,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score